# API Configuration
# ==================
# AUTO-DETECTION (Works on ANY WiFi!)
# Leave commented out below - api.ts will auto-detect your computer IP from Expo
# This works on: home WiFi, office WiFi, mobile hotspot, anywhere!

# For production/APK: uncomment the Vercel line
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://muscle-garage-3rgl.vercel.app/api

# For local development: leave EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL undefined
# and api.ts will auto-detect your computer's IP automatically!
